1. Ja sam napravila *tortu* za rođendan (I made a cake for the birthday).
2. Da li bi hteo/htela da probaš *tortu* od čokolade? (Would you like to try a chocolate cake?)
3. Na stolu se nalazila ogromna *torta*. (There was a huge cake on the table.)
4. Kada smo otišli u posetu babi, ona je uvek spremala najbolju *tortu*. (When we visited our grandma, she always made the best cake.)
5. Već dva dana jedem ovu *tortu* i još uvek mi nije dosadila. (I've been eating this cake for two days and I'm not tired of it yet.)
6. Nisam sigurna da li da kupim čokoladnu *tortu* ili voćnu *tortu* za proslavu rođendana. (I'm not sure whether to buy a chocolate cake or a fruit cake for the birthday party.)
7. Ne sviđa mi se previše ova *torta*. (I don't really like this cake.)
8. Kada sam bila mala, moja mama mi je uvek pravila *tortu* od jagoda za moj rođendan. (When I was a kid, my mom always made me a strawberry cake for my birthday.)
9. Njegova mama pravi najbolju *tortu* na svetu. (His mom makes the best cake in the world.)
10. Ova *torta* izgleda veoma ukusno. (This cake looks very delicious.)